[[File:BobaFettAirspeederModel-AotCTVD.jpg|thumb|[[Boba Fett/Legends|Boba Fett's]] toy painted in the colors of a Darien lava-skimmer]]
A '''Darien lava-skimmer''' was an entity<ref name="Dictionary">''[[Star Wars: Attack of the Clones: The Visual Dictionary]]''</ref> originating in the [[Darie system/Legends|Darie system]].<ref name="Planetnamia">{{JCFCite|url=posts/27848315|board=Literature|thread=The Essential Atlas and Galactic Cartography: Official Discussion|user=[[Jason Fry|jasonfry]]|date=2007-12-11|time=7:59 AM|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170916153037/http://boards.theforce.net/threads/the-essential-atlas-and-galactic-cartography-official-discussion.21938930/page-43|quote=I wouldn't get your hopes up re alien homeworlds, beyond simple stuff like the Planetnamian species getting a Planetnamia on the map or things Dan and I can account for with a relatively quick reference.|archivefile=File:JasonFry-JCFAtlasHomeworlds.png}} [[Jason Fry]], co-author of ''[[The Essential Atlas]]'', stated his intention to create [[Homeworld/Legends|homeworlds]] for numerous [[Species/Legends|species]] based on context implied from their names. Given this principle, this article makes a similar basic assumption for the Darien [[Magma/Legends|lava]]-skimmer in relation to the [[Darie system/Legends|Darie system]].</ref> It had an [[Color/Legends|orange]]-and-green color scheme. A toy model of an [[Airspeeder/Legends|airspeeder]] that [[Boba Fett/Legends|Boba Fett]] owned on [[Kamino/Legends|Kamino]] was painted in the colors of a Darien [[Magma/Legends|lava]]-skimmer.<ref name="Dictionary" />

